text: The 2024–25 Austrian Cup is the 94th edition of the national cup in Austrian football. SK Sturm Graz are the defending champions. ==First round == == Second round == The games of Rapid, LASK and Salzburg were postponed due to the international qualifiers. == Round of 16 == == Quarterfinals == == Semifinals== ==Final == ==References == Category:Austrian Cup Category:2024 in European sport Category:2025 in European sport Category:2025 in association football Category:2024 in association football Category:2024 in Austria
